data.description: Nicely updated Johnsburg residence featuring generously sized living areas, an expansive open-plan kitchen. Home freshly painted inside and out. Newer carpet throughout. Abundant natural light fills the space, accentuating the airy and roomy layout. Step outside to a fantastic deck that overlooks the backyard, which seamlessly blends into a picturesque nature reserve. Ideal for year-round outdoor enjoyment and various activities.
